<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>Fairfield County Tobacco Retail Surveillance Map</title>

<style>
:root {
  --navy: #0b3367;
  --gold: #d0b587;
  --goldSoft: #efe4d1;
  --ink: #16253a;
  --panel: #ffffff;
  --line: #d8e0ec;
  --bg: #f5f7fb;
  --blueSoft: #e8eef8;
  --greenSoft: #e3efe9;
  --shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(11, 51, 103, 0.08);
}

* {
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
  color: var(--ink);
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(208, 181, 135, 0.18), transparent 28%),
    linear-gradient(180deg, #eef3f9 0%, #f7f9fc 45%, #f6f8fb 100%);
}

.container {
  width: min(1220px, calc(100% - 32px));
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.hero {
  padding: 28px 0 18px;
}

.heroCard {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(11, 51, 103, 0.98), rgba(18, 63, 127, 0.97));
  color: #ffffff;
  border-radius: 28px;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  padding: 30px;
}

.kicker {
  display: inline-block;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
  border-radius: 999px;
  padding: 8px 14px;
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}

h1 {
  font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 58px);
  line-height: 1;
  margin: 0 0 14px;
  font-weight: 800;
}

.heroSub {
  font-size: 18px;
  line-height: 1.55;
  max-width: 900px;
  margin: 0;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.94);
}

.metricRow {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
  gap: 14px;
  margin-top: 22px;
}

.metric {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
  border-radius: 18px;
  padding: 16px 18px;
}

.metricLabel {
  font-size: 13px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.8px;
  opacity: 0.84;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}

.metricValue {
  font-size: 30px;
  font-weight: 800;
}

.metricNote {
  font-size: 14px;
  margin-top: 6px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
}

.section {
  padding: 18px 0;
}

.gridTwo {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 18px;
}

.panel {
  background: var(--panel);
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius: 24px;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  padding: 22px;
}

.panel h2 {
  margin: 0 0 8px;
  font-size: clamp(28px, 3vw, 40px);
  color: var(--navy);
}

.panelIntro {
  margin: 0 0 16px;
  font-size: 16px;
  line-height: 1.6;
  color: #40506b;
}

.calloutGrid {
  display: grid;
  gap: 14px;
}

.callout {
  border-radius: 18px;
  padding: 18px;
  line-height: 1.55;
}

.callout strong {
  display: block;
  color: var(--navy);
  margin-bottom: 6px;
  font-size: 18px;
}

.callout p {
  margin: 0;
}

.calloutOne {
  background: var(--goldSoft);
}

.calloutTwo {
  background: var(--blueSoft);
}

.calloutThree {
  background: var(--greenSoft);
}

.mapPanel {
  background: var(--panel);
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius: 24px;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  padding: 18px;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.mapFrame {
  width: 100%;
  height: 620px;
  border: 0;
  border-radius: 18px;
  display: block;
}

.legendRow {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 12px;
  margin-top: 14px;
}

.legendItem {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  background: #f4f6fa;
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius: 999px;
  padding: 9px 12px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--navy);
}

.dot {
  width: 14px;
  height: 14px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  display: inline-block;
}

.dotBlue {
  background: #17206d;
}

.dotGold {
  background: #f4b02f;
}

.footer {
  padding: 16px 0 34px;
}

.footerCard {
  background: #ebf0f7;
  border: 1px solid #d7e0ee;
  border-radius: 20px;
  padding: 18px 20px;
  color: #40506b;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

.noteTitle {
  font-weight: 800;
  color: var(--navy);
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}

@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .metricRow {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
  }

  .gridTwo {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }

  .mapFrame {
    height: 520px;
  }
}

@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .container {
    width: min(100% - 18px, 1220px);
  }

  .heroCard,
  .panel,
  .mapPanel {
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 18px;
  }

  .metricRow {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }

  .mapFrame {
    height: 460px;
  }
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="heroCard">
      <div class="kicker">Fairfield County Health Department</div>
      <h1>Tobacco Retail Surveillance Map</h1>
      <p class="heroSub">
        This page provides a visual summary of tobacco compliance check locations and store audit locations across Fairfield County. The map can support planning, documentation, coverage review, and partner conversations.
      </p>

      <div class="metricRow">
        <div class="metric">
          <div class="metricLabel">Compliance check locations</div>
          <div class="metricValue">54</div>
          <div class="metricNote">Mapped in the current layer</div>
        </div>

        <div class="metric">
          <div class="metricLabel">Store audit locations</div>
          <div class="metricValue">53</div>
          <div class="metricNote">Mapped in the current layer</div>
        </div>

        <div class="metric">
          <div class="metricLabel">Map layers</div>
          <div class="metricValue">2</div>
          <div class="metricNote">Compliance checks and store audits</div>
        </div>

        <div class="metric">
          <div class="metricLabel">Last updated</div>
          <div class="metricValue">Nov 18, 2025</div>
          <div class="metricNote">Based on the current Google My Maps file</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="section">
  <div class="container gridTwo">
    <div class="panel">
      <h2>Why this matters</h2>
      <p class="panelIntro">
        Tobacco retail surveillance activities help document where checks and audits are occurring and support more informed planning across the county.
      </p>

      <div class="calloutGrid">
        <div class="callout calloutOne">
          <strong>Planning support</strong>
          <p>This map can help staff review geographic coverage and identify areas that may need additional attention during future planning.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="callout calloutTwo">
          <strong>Documentation</strong>
          <p>The map provides a clear visual reference for sites included in compliance check and store audit tracking.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="callout calloutThree">
          <strong>Partner communication</strong>
          <p>The page can be shared as a simple visual summary when discussing tobacco retail monitoring activities with leadership or partners.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="panel">
      <h2>How to use this map</h2>
      <p class="panelIntro">
        Use the map tools to zoom, search, and turn layers on or off. Click individual points to view location details.
      </p>

      <div class="legendRow">
        <div class="legendItem">
          <span class="dot dotBlue"></span>
          Compliance check locations
        </div>

        <div class="legendItem">
          <span class="dot dotGold"></span>
          Store audit locations
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="mapPanel">
      <iframe
        class="mapFrame"
        src="https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/0/embed?mid=1xOu5nDnY5vgCYaelEpMeFXHYxugQZC4&ehbc=2E312F"
        allowfullscreen>
      </iframe>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="footer">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="footerCard">
      <span class="noteTitle">Interpretation note</span>
      Mapped locations represent sites included in the current tracking file. This map should not be interpreted as a complete list of all tobacco retailers unless the source list has been confirmed as complete and current.
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
